}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "WA3001A Rev:T3.0" is silkscreened on the main board in the FCC photos. "Eumitcom Technology Inc." and "WL11000RFM Rev: T3.0" is silkscreened on the RF module.
There is no HTTP configuration interface for this device. You will be required to use [http://en-us-support.belkin.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/3471 Eumitcom's Access Point manager] software.
